ng%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20can't%20lose%20this%20moment%26quot%3B%20to%20seize%20the%20chance%20for%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20has%20offered%20a%20comprehensive%20new%20proposal.%20It's%20a%20roadmap%20to%20an%20enduring%20ceasefire%20and%20the%20release%20of%20all%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2081-year-old%20Democrat%20put%20particular%20pressure%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%2C%20whose%20attack%20on%20key%20US%20ally%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20last%20year%20trigged%20the%20grinding%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20needs%20to%20take%20the%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Biden%2C%20who%20has%20supported%20Israel%20with%20military%20aid%20since%20the%20conflict%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20the%20first%20six-week%20phase%20would%20include%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull%20and%20complete%20ceasefire%2C%20withdrawal%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20from%20all%20populated%20areas%20of%20Gaza%2C%20release%20of%20a%20number%20of%20hostages%2C%20including%20women%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20the%20wounded%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20release%20of%20hundreds%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20the%20Palestinians%20would%20then%20negotiate%20during%20those%20six%20weeks%20for%20a%20lasting%20ceasefire%20--%20but%20the%20truce%20would%20continue%20if%20the%20talks%20remained%20underway%2C%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20Hamas%20lives%20up%20to%20its%20commitments%2C%20a%20temporary%20ceasefire%20would%20become%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20the%20Israeli%20proposal%2C%20the%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%20permanently%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sheer%20hell'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20announcement%20of%20the%20proposal%20comes%20after%20repeated%20attempts%20to%20end%20the%20war%20have%20stalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20insists%20that%20any%20ceasefire%20should%20be%20permanent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20said%20earlier%20Friday%20it%20had%20informed%20mediators%20it%20would%20only%20agree%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%26quot%3B%20truce%20agreement%20including%20a%20hostage-prisoner%20swap%20if%20Israel%20halts%20its%20%26quot%3Baggression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsmail%20Haniyeh%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Hamas's%20Qatar-based%20political%20office%2C%20reiterated%20that%20the%20group's%20core%20demands%20--%20including%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%20and%20full%20Israeli%20withdrawal%20--%20%26quot%3Bare%20non-negotiable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Israel%20says%20it%20will%20only%20agree%20to%20a%20temporary%20truce%20of%20around%20six%20weeks%20and%20that%20it%20maintains%20its%20aim%20of%20destroying%20the%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20did%20not%20significantly%20address%20Israel's%20assault%20on%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20city%20of%20Rafah%2C%20into%20whose%20central%20area%20the%20Israeli%20army%20said%20Friday%20its%20troops%20had%20pushed%20into%20despite%20international%20objections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20however%20that%20Palestinians%20were%20enduring%20%26quot%3Bsheer%20hell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20president%20has%20been%20under%20growing%20pressure%20over%20his%20support%20for%20Israel%20since%20a%20deadly%20strike%20on%20Rafah%20set%20ablaze%20a%20crowded%20camp%20on%20Sunday.%20Gaza%20officials%20said%2045%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20about%20250%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20however%20said%20this%20week%20that%20while%20the%20Israeli%20strike%20was%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20did%20not%20breach%20Biden's%20red%20lines%20for%20withholding%20weapons%20deliveries%20to%20the%20key%20US%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3