2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hearing%20took%20place%20before%20the%20JJ%20board%20and%20it%20allowed%20our%20plea%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shailesh%20Balkawade%2C%20Additional%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(crime).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20claim%20the%20teenager%20was%20driving%20the%20luxury%20car%20in%20an%20inebriated%20state%20when%20it%20hit%20two%20IT%20professionals%20on%20a%20motorbike%20in%20the%20city's%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20area%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20May%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%2C%20inquiry%20of%20a%20minor%20has%20to%20be%20conducted%20in%20the%20parents'%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JJB%20granted%20bail%20to%20the%20teenager%2C%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20real%20estate%20developer%2C%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20May%2019%20crash%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20road%20safety.%20Amid%20a%20nationwide%20outcry%2C%20police%20again%20approached%20the%20JJB%2C%20which%20modified%20the%20order%20and%20sent%20him%20to%20the%20observation%20home%20till%20June%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20bail%20was%20given%20to%20the%20juvenile%20by%20a%20single%20member%20of%20the%20JJ%20Board%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20JJB%20members%20and%20check%20if%20norms%20were%20followed%20while%20issuing%20orders%20in%20the%20Pune%20car%20crash%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20a%20deputy%20commissioner%2C%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20next%20week%2C%20said%20Prashant%20Narnavare%2C%20commissioner%20of%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JJB%20comprises%20a%20member%20from%20the%20judiciary%20and%20two%20persons%20appointed%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20current%20inquiry%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20probe%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20state-appointed%20members%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minor's%20father%20and%20grandfather%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20wrongfully%20confining%20the%20family's%20driver%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20offering%20him%20cash%20and%20gifts%20for%20taking%20the%20blame%20(and%20shielding%20the%20minor)%2C%20and%20also%20threatening%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20arrested%20two%20doctors%20and%20a%20staffer%20from%20Sassoon%20General%20Hospital%20here%20for%20allegedly%20manipulating%20the%20teenager's%20blood%20samples%20to%20show%20that%20he%20was%20not%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20on%20Friday%20moved%20an%20application%20for%20custody%20of%20the%20teenager's%20father%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20switching%20of%20the%20blood%20samples.%20Earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20(First%20Class)%20AA%20Pande%20remanded%20the%20real%20estate%20developer%20and%20his%20father%20(the%20minor's%20grandfather)%20in%20judicial%20custody%20for%2014%20days%20after%20their%20police%20custody%20in%20the%20driver%20kidnapping%20case%20got%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20police%2C%20about%20a%20dozen%20calls%20were%20exchanged%20between%20the%20juvenile's%20father%20and%20Dr%20Ajay%20Taware%2C%20one%20of%20the%20arrested%20doctors%2C%20while%20samples%20were%20being%20collected%20for%20testing%20for%20alcohol%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717173720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fadso2k18_pune-porsche-_625x300_20_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjuvenile-board-allows-pune-cops-to-investigate-minor-in-porsche-case-5789092%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20(JJB)%20here%20on%20Friday%20allowed%20police%20to%20investigat