borrowing-limit-in-foreign-currency-to-24-bn-124053101727_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Bakes%20At%2045.8%20Degrees%2C%20Sees%20Driest%20May%20In%2010%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20capital%20reeled%20under%20heat%20wave%20conditions%20for%20the%20fifth%20day%20on%20Friday%20with%20the%20mercury%20soaring%20to%2045.8%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20six%20notches%20above%20normal%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20department%20also%20said%20the%20national%20capital%20recorded%20only%20two%20rainy%20days%20this%20May%2C%20the%20lowest%20in%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20issued%20a%20'yellow%20alert'%20for%20Saturday%20and%20predicted%20generally%20cloudy%20skies%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20thunderstorms%20and%20dust%20storms%20accompanied%20by%20light%20showers%20and%20gusty%20winds%20at%20speeds%20of%2030%20to%2040%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maximum%20and%20minimum%20temperatures%20are%20likely%20to%20reach%2044%20and%2020%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MeT%20has%20four%20colour-coded%20warnings%20--%20green%20(no%20action%20needed)%2C%20yellow%20(watch%20and%20stay%20updated)%2C%20orange%20(be%20prepared)%20and%20red%20(take%20action).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriday's%20mercury%20reading%20is%20the%20second-highest%20maximum%20temperature%20recorded%20by%20Delhi's%20primary%20weather%20station%2C%20the%20Safdarjung%20Observatory%2C%20this%20summer%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MeT%20said%20the%20minimum%20was%20recorded%20at%2029%20degrees%20Celsius.%20The%20city's%20relative%20humidity%20oscillated%20between%2038%20per%20cent%20and%2023%20per%20cent%20during%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20broke%20its%20temperature%20records%20this%20month%2C%20noting%20a%2079-year%20high%20of%2046.8%20degrees%20Celsius%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20IMD%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2017%2C%201945%2C%20the%20national%20capital%20noted%20a%20maximum%20temperature%20of%2046.7%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Mungeshpur%20recorded%2052.9%20degrees%20Celsius.%20The%20IMD%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20they%20are%20examining%20the%20sensors%20and%20data%20of%20the%20area's%20weather%20station%20for%20any%20potential%20errors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20weather%20department%20has%20not%20yet%20issued%20any%20report%20on%20the%20inspection%20of%20the%20sensors%20in%20Mungeshpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20capital%20is%20also%20facing%20water%20shortage%20due%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20summer%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20month%20also%20saw%20the%20least%20number%20of%20rainy%20days%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Delhi%20saw%20only%20two%20rainy%20days%20this%20May%2C%20compared%20to%2011%20in%202023%2C%20seven%20in%202022%2C%2012%20in%202021%2C%20and%20seven%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20maximum%20and%20minimum%20temperatures%20in%20May%20stood%20at%2041.4%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%2026.5%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20respectively%2C%20the%20weather%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMD%2C%20the%20threshold%20for%20a%20heatwave%20is%20met%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20a%20weather%20station%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20plains%2C%2037%20degrees%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20and%2030%20degrees%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%2C%20and%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20is%20at%20least%204.5%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20severe%20heat%20wave%20is%20declared%20if%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20exceeds%206.4%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717168020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.