short%20of%20the%20majority%20of%20272%20and%20well%20below%20its%20ambitious%20'%3Cem%3Eabki%20baar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20400%20%3Cem%3Epaar%3C%2Fem%3E'%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFascinating...%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20has%20revised%20his%20earlier%20estimates%20and%20now%20says%20the%20BJP%20will%20definitely%20fall%20short%20of%20272.%20He%20tells%20Karan%20Thapar%20the%20BJP%20could%20go%20down%20to%20250%20but%2C%20if%20the%20undercurrent%20is%20strong%20(referring%20to%20anti-incumbency)%20it%20could%20even%20fall%20to%20230%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Yadav%20says%20he%20expects%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20NDA%20to%20win%2035%20to%2040%20seats.%20This%20means%20if%20the%20BJP%20were%20to%20fall%20as%20low%20as%20230%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%2C%20even%20with%20support%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20to%20reach%20the%20majority%20mark.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInteresting%20times%20ahead%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20he%20took%20a%20dig%20of%20his%20own%2C%20saying%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwondering-whether-bjp-will-be-able-to-get-200-paar-shashi-tharoor-5766907%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewondered%20if%20the%20BJP%20could%20win%20even%20200%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bearlier%20estimated%26quot%3B%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20referred%20to%20was%20an%20interview%20last%20week%20in%20which%20Mr%20Yadav%20suggested%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20cross%20the%20300-seat%20mark%20as%20it%20did%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThanks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShashiTharoor%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ShashiTharoor%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20noticing%20what%20I%20say%20to%20Karan%20Thapar.%3Cbr%3E%5