bs%2C%206%20Home%20Guards%20On%20Poll%20Duty%20Die%20In%20UP%2C%2017%20Hospitalised%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20unprecedented%20heat%20wave%20across%20north%20India%20has%20cost%20the%20lives%20of%20dozens%20including%20that%20of%20six%20Home%20Guards%20who%20were%20on%20election%20duty%20in%20Mirzapur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20There%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20multiple%20deaths%20in%20Rajasthan%20as%20well%2C%20though%20the%20official%20figure%20is%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERB%20Kamal%2C%20the%20Principal%20of%20Mirzapur%20Medical%20College%20said%20six%20of%2023%20Home%20Guards%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%20have%20died.%20All%20of%20them%20were%20admitted%20with%20other%20complaints%20--%20including%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20heart%20problems%20and%20other%20diseases.%20Currently%2C%20the%20condition%20of%20two%20jawans%20is%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwenty-three%20people%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20us%20so%20far%20among%20whom%20one%20is%20from%20Fire%20Service%20and%20one%20from%20civil%20police.%20There%20were%2020%20jawans%20from%20the%20Home%20Guard.%20Six%20jawans%20have%20died.%20Two%20are%20critical%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20symptoms%2C%20he%20said%20they%20were%20brought%20in%20with%20high%20grade%20fever%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20high%20blood%20sugar.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20high%20chance%20of%20brain%20stroke%2C%20which%20could%20be%20fatal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20week%2C%20as%20temperature%20across%20north%20India%20shot%20onto%20unprecedented%20levels%2C%20unconfirmed%20reports%20of%20multiple%20deaths%20of%20homeless%20people%20have%20been%20flowing%20in.%20Unidentified%20bodies%20have%20been%20piling%20up%20in%20morgues%20and%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20postmortems%20reports%20are%20awaited%20to%20confirm%20the%20cause%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20got%20so%20alarming%20that%20yesterday%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court%20took%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20deaths%20and%20urged%20the%20Centre%20to%20declare%20the%20ongoing%20heat%20wave%20as%20a%20national%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20pay%20compensation%20to%20the%20victims'%20families%20and%20issued%20several%20guidelines%20to%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20things%2C%20the%20court%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20sprinkle%20water%20on%20roads%2C%20mark%20out%20shaded%20areas%20and%20distribute%20water%2C%20ORS%20and%20cooling%20drinks%20like%20mango%20panna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabourers%2C%20cart%20and%20rickshaw%20pullers%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20rest%20between%20noon%20and%203%20pm%2C%20the%20court%20said.%20Heat%20alerts%20should%20also%20be%20sent%20through%20bulk%20messages%2C%20print%20and%20electronic%20media%20to%20caution%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717166820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fkjuhbo1o_heat-wave-generic-summer-weather-generic-ani_625x300_07_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-mercury-climbs-6-home-guards-on-poll-duty-die-in-up-17-hospitalised-5788280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unprecedented%20heat%20wave%20across%20north%20India%20has%20cost%20the%20lives%20of%20dozens%20including%20that%20of%20six%20Home%20Guards%20who%20were%20on%20election%20duty%20in%20Mirzapur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20There%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20multiple%20deaths%20in%20Rajasthan%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-mercury-climbs-6-home-guards-on-poll-duty-die-in-up-17-hospitalised-5788280%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-mercury-climbs-6-home-guards-on-poll-duty-die-in-up-