%3Cp%3EThe%20Shigatse%20airbase%20has%20been%20significantly%20upgraded%20over%20the%20last%203%20years.%20High-res%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4scjsqqg_full-airbase-main-650-_650x400_31_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%2012%2C408%20feet%2C%20Shigatse%2C%20the%20second%20largest%20city%20in%20Tibet%2C%20has%20a%20dual-use%20airport%20for%20civil%20and%20military%20use.%20The%20deployment%20of%20the%20J-20%20shows%20its%20ability%20to%20operate%20from%20the%20harsh%20environment%20of%20ultra-high%20altitude%20Tibetan%20air%20bases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20the%20fighters%20also%20indicate%20that%20the%20Chinese%20Air%20Force%20may%20have%20deployed%20infrastructure%20to%20sustain%20operations%20of%20the%20fighters%20in%20the%20area%20before%20a%20possible%20full-fledged%2C%20permanent%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20has%20declined%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20J-20%20deployment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20forward%20presence%20of%20the%20J-20%20in%20Tibetan%20airfields%20is%20a%20clear%20and%20present%20threat%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20This%20erodes%20the%20advantage%20enjoyed%20by%20IAF%20assets%20like%20the%20Rafale%20and%20imposes%20caution%20against%20the%20PLAAF%20%5BChinese%20Air%20Force%5D%2C''%20says%20Sameer%20Joshi%2C%20a%20former%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20now%20the%20CEO%20of%20NewSpace%20Research%20which%20is%20developing%20drones%20for%20the%20Indian%20Armed%20forces.%20''This%20capability%2C%20combined%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20available%20numbers%20of%20modern%20fighters%20in%20the%20Chinese%20inventory%2C%20clearly%20negates%20the%20numerical%20advantage%20in%20modern%20jets%20that%20the%20IAF%20has%20enjoyed%20for%20some%20time.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20shown%20in%20this%20report%2C%20captured%20on%20May%2027%2C%20show%20a%20J-20%20deploying%20its%20drogue%20parachute%20to%20slow%20down%20upon%20landing%20at%20Shigatse%2C%20as%20other%20J-20s%20taxi%20to%20the%20flight-line.%20Another%20image%20shows%20a%20J-20%20moving%20past%20a%20couple%20of%20Chinese%20F-7s%2C%20a%20license-built%20variant%20of%20Russia's%20venerable%20MiG-21.%20China%20began%20domestic%20manufacture%20of%20the%20J-7%20in%201964.%20Its%20new%20J-20%20stealth%20fighter%20first%20flew%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Satellite%20imagery%20from%20May%2027%20captured%20a%20J-20%20having%20deployed%20its%20brake%20parachute%20upon%20landing%20in%20Shigatse.%20High-res%20here%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Satellite%20imagery%20from%20May%2027%20captured%20a%20J-20%20having%20deployed%20its%20brake%20parachute%20upon%20landing%20in%20Shigatse.%20High-res%20here%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpn085jjg_j20-drag-chute_625x300_31_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20imagery%20from%20May%2027%20captured%20a%20J-20%20having%20deployed%20its%20brake%20parachute%20upon%20landing%20in%20Shigatse.%20High-res%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fotb9e0pg_full-airbase-02-650-_650x400_31_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20J-20%20stealth%20fighter%20is%20China's%20most%20advanced%20operational%20fighter%20aircraft%20to%20date%2C%20and%20these%20aircraft%20are%20predominantly%20based%20in%20the%20eastern%20provinces%20of%20China%2C''%20according%20to%20Sim%20Tack%2C%20a%20Geospatial%20analyst%20with%20All%20Source%20Analysis%2C%20which%20first%20reported%20the%20deployment%20of%20the%20J-20s%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%20in%20Shigatse.%20''Seeing%20these%20aircraft%20appear%20at%20Shigatse%20in%20Tibet%20positions%20them%20on%20a%20deployment%20outside%20of%20their%20normal%20areas%20of%20operations%20and%20within%20proximity%20of%20the%20Indian%20border.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20the%20J-20%20has%20been%20deployed%20in%20Tibet.%20The%20jets%20have%20been%20observed%20in%20Xinjiang%20in%20China's%20Hotan%20prefecture%20between%202020%20and%202023.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20deployment%20of%20the%20J-20%20which%20has%20been%20spotted%20by%20commercially%20available%20satellite%20imagery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20deployment%20of%20the%20J-20%20in%20Shigatse%20is%20meant%20to%20send%20India%20a%20message%20says%20Commodore%20TJ%20Maolankar%20(retired)%2C%20a%20former%20Chief%20Test%20pilot%20on%20India's%20Tejas%20fighter%20which%20he%20landed%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20on%20India's%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20INS%20Vikramaditya.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''On%20the%20one%20hand%20it%20clearly%20demonstrates%20that%20the%20Chinese%20have%20fully%20incorporated%20significant%20combat%20aviation%20into%20their%20frontline%20capabilities%20over%20the%20Himalayas.%20On%20the%20other%20it%20underscores%20yet%20again%20the%20unavoidable%20vulnerability%20of%20fixed%20airfields.%20Is%20it%20that%20the%20Chinese%20don't%20mind%20showing%20them%20off%20like%20this%20because%20they%20do%20not%20believe%20we%20have%20the%20means%20or%20the%20will%20to%20strike%20at%20them%20first%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chengdu%20J-20%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Mighty%20Dragon%2C%20is%20a%20twin-engine%20stealth%20fighter%20which%20was%20introduced%20into%20service%20in%202017.%20With%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20fighter%2C%20China%20emerged%20as%20the%20third%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20operationally%20field%20stealth%20fighters.%20The%20jet%2C%20which%20is%20equipped%20with%20an%20array%20of%20sensors%2C%20is%20being%20constantly%20modernised.%20Its%20primary%20role%20is%20as%20an%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20and%20it%20carries%20China's%20most%20advanced%20air%20to%20air%20missiles%2C%20including%20the%20PL-15%20long%20range%20air%20to%20air%20missile%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20the%20ability%20of%20striking%20aerial%20targets%20upto%20300%20kilometres%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20J-20%20stealth%20fighter%20moves%20past%20an%20obsolete%20J-7%20jet%2C%20a%20Chinese%20variant%20of%20the%20Russian%20MiG-21.%20High-res%20here%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20J-20%20stealth%20fighter%20moves%20past%20an%20obsolete%20J-7%20jet%2C%20a%20Chinese%20variant%20of%20the%20Russian%20MiG-21.%20High-res%20here%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fese2c4i8_full3_625x300_31_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20J-20%20stealth%20fighter%20moves%20past%20an%20obsolete%20J-7%20jet%2C%20a%20Chinese%20variant%20of%20the%20Russian%20MiG-21.%20High-res%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmcq1q86o_full-airbase-03-650-_650x400_31_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOperating%20in%20conjunction%20with%20drones%2C%20airborne%20warning%20aircraft%20and%20electronic%20warning%20platforms%2C%20the%20J-20%20will%20be%20able%20to%20''deploy%20quickly%20over%20large%20swathes%20of%20Tibet%20in%20a%20fused%20awareness%20spectrum%2C%20helping%20operationalise%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20an%20'intelligentised'%20large%20area%20defensive%20doctrine%20for%20the%20PLAAF%2C''%20says%20Sameer%20Joshi.%20%C2%A0In%20simple%20terms%2C%20this%20means%20that%20the%20J-20%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20operate%20as%20a%20key%20part%20of%20a%20deeply%20networked%20and%20electronically%20enabled%20force%20which%20uses%20several%20new%20aviation%20assets%20including%20state%20of%20the%20art%20drones%2C%20new%20generation%20fighters%20and%20older%20assets%2C%20connected%20electronically%20through%20data-links%20which%20enable%20the%20force%20to%20deploy%20together%20as%20a%20cohesive%20warfighting%20unit.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''China%20has%20steadily%20built%20up%20its%20air%20power%20capacity%20in%20Tibet%20and%20other%20areas%20near%20India%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20This%20has%20primarily%20consisted%20of%20the%20construction%20of%20new%20air%20bases%20and%20upgrading%20the%20infrastructure%20at%20existing%20air%20bases%2C''%20says%20Sim%20Tack.%20China%20has%20also%20begun%20deploying%20aircraft%20such%20as%20the%20J-20%20and%20its%20H-6%20nuclear-capable%20bombers%20to%20these%20border%20regions%2C%20at%20least%20on%20a%20temporary%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20matches%20this%20Chinese%20airfield%20expansion%20by%20significantly%20upgrading%20its%20own%20airbases%20with%20hardened%20shelters%20for%20its%20aircraft%20in%20addition%20to%20expanding%20its%20tiered%20surface-to-air%20missile%20defences%2C%20which%20has%20included%20the%20deployment%20of%20the%20Russian-built%20S-400%20long%20range%20surface%20to%20air%20missile%20system%20in%20Eastern%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shigatse%20airbase%20lies%20less%20than%20300%20kilometres%20from%20Indias%20second%20Rafale%20airbase%20in%20Hasimara%2C%20Bengal%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Shigatse%20airbase%20lies%20less%20than%20300%20kilometres%20from%20Indias%20second%20Rafale%20airbase%20in%20Hasimara%2C%20Bengal%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fh261oob8_shigatse-hasimara-map_625x300_31_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shigatse%20airbase%20lies%20less%20than%20300%20kilometres%20from%20India's%20second%20Rafale%20airbase%20in%20Hasimara%2C%20Bengal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deployment%20of%20the%20S-400%20system%2C%20which%20reportedly%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20track%20stealth%20platforms%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20deter%20offensive%20Chinese%20fighter-sweeps%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20key%20part%20of%20India's%20defences%2C%20the%20S-400%2C%20acquired%20from%20Russia%20in%20a%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20(%245.43%20billion)%20deal%20signed%20in%202018%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20be%20vulnerable%20while%20under%20attack%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20Most%20recently%2C%20a%20video%20has%20emerged%20of%20an%20S-400%20unit%20composed%20of%20radars%2C%20missile%20launchers%20and%20other%20vehicles%20being%20destroyed%20by%20Ukrainian-launched%20ATACMS%20ballistic%20missiles%20which%20it%20was%2C%20evidently%2C%20unable%20to%20intercept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20both%20China%20and%20India%20operate%20the%20same%20S-400%20missile%20system%2C%20imported%20from%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717162740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F42oc10ko_fullairbase01correction1200_625x300_31_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-counters-indias-rafale-with-stealth-jet-deployment-near-sikkim-5786350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%2C%20high%20resolution%20satellite%20imagery%20available%20with%20NDTV%20show%20several%20J-20s%2C%20China's%20most%20advanced%20stealth%20fighter%2C%20landing%20at%20a%20key%20high-altitude%20Tibetan%20air%20base%20located%20less%20than%20150%20kilometres%20from%20the%20Sikkim%20border.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-counters-indias-rafale-with-stealth-jet-deployment-near-sikkim-5786350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-counters-indias-rafale-with-stealth-jet-deployment-near-sikkim-5786350%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-counters-indias-rafale-with-stealth-jet-deployment-near-sikkim-5786350%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2