2Fparting-ways-with-rohit-sharma-and-ex-india-star-on-2-players-mumbai-indians-might-release-5771806%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fparting-ways-with-rohit-sharma-and-ex-india-star-on-2-players-mumbai-indians-might-release-5771806%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fparting-ways-with-rohit-sharma-and-ex-india-star-on-2-players-mumbai-indians-might-release-5771806%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BData%20Void%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BInformation%20Gap%26quot%3B%3A%20Google%20Explains%20AI%20Search's%20Odd%20Results%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20week%20after%20a%20series%20of%20screenshots%20of%20Google's%20artificial%20intelligence%20search%20tool%20-%20AI%20Overviews%20-%20providing%20inaccurate%20responses%20made%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Google%20has%20issued%20an%20explanation%20and%20cited%20%26quot%3Bdata%20void%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binformation%20gap%26quot%3B%20as%20reasons%20behind%20the%20blunder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20weeks%20ago%2C%20Google%20rolled%20out%20its%20experimental%20AI%20search%20feature%20in%20the%20US%2C%20however%2C%20it%20soon%20faced%20scrutiny%20after%20people%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20the%20bizarre%20responses%20by%20the%20search%20tool%2C%20including%20telling%20people%20to%20eat%20rocks%20and%20mix%20pizza%20cheese%20with%20glue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blogpost%2C%20Google%20acknowledged%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20odd%2C%20inaccurate%20or%20unhelpful%20AI%20Overviews%20certainly%20did%20show%20up%26quot%3B%20while%20also%20debunking%20the%20alleged%20dangerous%20responses%20on%20topics%20such%20as%20leaving%20dogs%20in%20cars%20and%20smoking%20while%20pregnant%20saying%20that%20those%20AI%20Overviews%20%26quot%3Bnever%20appeared%26quot%3B.%20Google%20also%20called%20out%20a%20large%20number%20of%20faked%20screenshots%20being%20shared%20online%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bobvious%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsilly%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20has%20said%20that%20they%20saw%20%26quot%3Bnonsensical%20new%20searches%2C%20seemingly%20aimed%20at%20producing%20erroneous%20results%26quot%3B%20and%20added%20that%20one%20of%20the%20areas%20it%20needed%20to%20improve%20in%20is%20interpreting%20nonsensical%20queries%20and%20satirical%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20example%20of%20a%20question%20in%20the%20viral%20screenshots%20-%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20rocks%20should%20I%20eat%3F%26quot%3B%20-%20Google%20said%20that%20practically%20no%20one%20asked%20that%20question%20before%20those%20screenshots%20went%20viral.%20Since%20not%20much%20high-quality%20web%20content%20that%20seriously%20contemplates%20that%20question%20is%20available%20online%2C%20it%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Bdata%20void%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Binformation%20gap%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Google.%20Explaining%20why%20the%20search%20tool%20came%20up%20with%20a%20bizarre%20response%20to%20this%20particular%20query%2C%20Google%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20satirical%20content%20on%20this%20topic%20...%20that%20also%20happened%20to%20be%20republished%20on%20a%20geological%20software%20provider's%20website.%20So%20when%20someone%20put%20that%20question%20into%20Search%2C%20an%20AI%20Overview%20appeared%20that%20faithfully%20linked%20to%20one%20of%20the%20only%20websites%20that%20tackled%20the%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20blogpost%2C%20Liz%20Reid%2C%20VP%2C%20Head%20of%20Google%20Search%20also%20explained%20how%20AI%20Overviews%20work%20and%20what%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20chatbots%20and%20other%20LLM%20products.%20She%20said%20that%20AI%20Overviews%20are%20%26quot%3Bpowered%20by%20a%20customized%20language%20model%2C%20which%20is%20integrated%20with%20our%20core%20web%20ranking%20systems%2C%20and%20are%20designed%20to%20carry%20out%20traditional%20%26quot%3Bsearch%26quot%3B%20tasks%2C%20like%20identifying%20relevant%2C%20high-quality%20results%20from%20Google's%20index.%26quot%3B%20That%20is%20why%2C%20AI%20Overviews%20don't%20just%20provide%20text%20output%20but%20also%20give%20relevant%20links%20that%20back%20the%20results%20and%20allow%20people%20to%20explore%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20AI%20Overviews%20generally%20don't%20%26quot%3Bhallucinate%26quot%3B%20or%20make%20things%20up%20in%20the%20ways%20that%20other%20LLM%20products%20might%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Google%2C%20when%20AI%20Overviews%20get%20something%20wrong%2C%20it%20is%20due%20to%20reasons%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bmisinterpreting%20queries%2C%20misinterpreting%20a%20nuance%20of%20language%20on%20the%20web%2C%20or%20not%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20information%20available.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20identifying%20patterns%20where%20Google%20got%20it%20wrong%2C%20the%20company%20has%20said%20it%20has%20made%20over%20a%20dozen%20technical%20improvements%20such%20as-%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGoogle%20has%20built%20better%20detection%20mechanisms%20for%20nonsensical%20queries%20and%20limited%20the%20inclusion%20of%20satire%20and%20humor%20content.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGoogle%20has%20updated%20its%20systems%20to%20limit%20the%20use%20of%20user-generated%20content%20in%20responses%20that%20could%20offer%20misleading%20advice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGoogle%20has%20added%20triggering%20restrictions%20for%20queries%20where%20AI%20Overviews%20were%20not%20proving%20to%20be%20as%20helpful.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAI%20Overviews%20for%20hard%20news%20topics%20will%20not%20be%20shown%20where%20%26quot%3Bfreshness%20and%20factuality%26quot%3B%20are%20crucial.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%20improvements%2C%20Google%20said%20that%20it%20has%20found%20content%20policy%20violation%20on%20%26quot%3Bless%20than%20one%20in%20every%207%20million%20unique%20queries%26quot%3B%20on%20which%20AI%20Overviews%20appeared%20and%20has%20taken%20action%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717161480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F40cmfqso_google-generic_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdata-void-information-gap-google-explains-ai-overviews-odd-results-5787757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20week%20after%20a%20series%20of%20screenshots%20of%20Google's%20artificial%20intelligence%20search%20tool%20-%20AI%20Overviews%20-%20providing%20inaccurate%20responses%20made%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Google%20has%20issued%20an%20explanation%20and%20cited%20%26quot%3Bdata%20void%26quot%3B%20as%20reason%20behind%20the%20blunder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdata-void-information-gap-google-explains-ai-overviews-odd-results-5787757%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdata-void-information-gap-google-explains-ai-overviews-odd-results-5787757%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdata-void-information-gap-google-explains-ai-overviews-odd-results-5787757%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%205%20killed%2C%2050%20injured%20in%20gas%20explosion%20due%20to%20hot%20weather%20in%20Pakistan's%20Sindh%3A%20Officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717161444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110598799%2Cimgsize-511697.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fat-least-5-killed-50-injured-in-gas-explosion-due-to-hot-weather-in-pakistans-sindh-officials%2Farticleshow%2F110598456.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphot