div%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EGlobal%20Risk%20Report%20202%3C%2Fem%3E4%20from%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20(WEF)%20states%20that%20misinformation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20threats%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20are%20faced%20with.%20India%2C%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20is%20identified%20as%20one%20of%20the%20nations%20with%20the%20most%20significant%20risks%20associated%20with%20disinformation%20and%20misinformation.%20This%20is%20particularly%20important%20as%20India%20concludes%20its%20national%20elections%20and%20over%2050%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20go%20to%20polls%20this%20year.%20What%20an%20unprecedented%20time%20and%20a%20test%20for%20democracies%20globally!%20There%20is%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20from%20Indian%20elections%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20misinformation%20vectors%20circulate%20in%20different%20formats%2C%20languages%20and%20regions%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20and%20information%20landscape%20is%20evolving%20rapidly%20in%20India%20as%20more%20and%20more%20people%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20mostly%20via%20their%20phones.%20Today%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Indians%20-%20870%20million%20people%20-%20are%20active%20internet%20users.%20This%20is%20creating%20a%20new%20challenge%20as%20reliable%20sources%20of%20news%20are%20frequently%20drowned%20out%20by%20unverified%20information%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20increasingly%20learning%20from%20elections%20worldwide%20that%20misinformation%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20deceive%20voters%20and%20undermine%20their%20trust%20in%20the%20electoral%20processes.%20People%20are%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20world%20with%20more%20choices%20for%20information%20than%20what%20was%20available%20at%20any%20point%20in%20human%20history.%20This%20creates%20a%20major%20problem%20as%20people%20struggle%20to%20distinguish%20between%20truthful%20and%20false%20information.%20Research%20says%20that%20the%20more%20individuals%20are%20exposed%20to%20falsehoods%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20they%20are%20to%20believe%20them%2C%20even%20when%20the%20information%20contradicts%20their%20existing%20beliefs.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20elections%20become%20a%20hotbed%20of%20contestations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commitment%20to%20preserving%20the%20values%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20sanctity%20of%20voters'%20decisions%20based%20on%20facts%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20Shakti-India%20Election%20Fact-Checking%20Collective%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Google%20News%20Initiative.%20It%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20DataLEADS%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Misinformation%20Combat%20Alliance%20(MCA)%2C%20%3Cem%3EBOOM%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Quint%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EVishvas%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EFactly%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewschecker%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20among%20other%20leading%20fact-checking%20organisations%20and%20news%20publishers%20like%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EPress%20Trust%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(PTI).%20The%20project%20is%20a%20coalition%20of%20Indian%20fact-checkers%20and%20publishers%20that%20came%20together%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20India%20elections%20to%20enhance%20the%20early%20detection%20of%20election-related%20misinformation%20and%20deepfakes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20amplify%20the%20dissemination%20of%20fact-checks%20in%20regional%20languages.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20collaboration%20so%20far%20in%20India%20between%20fact-checkers%20and%20publishers%20to%20fight%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Shakti%20Collective%2C%20it%20was%20incredible%20to%20see%20how%20diverse%20news%20organisations%2C%20including%20competitors%2C%20came%20together%20to%20address%20misinformation.%20Nearly%2050-plus%20organisations%2C%20comprising%20prominent%20fact-checkers%20and%20established%20newsrooms%2C%20big%20and%20small%2C%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20joined%20hands%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20collective.%20Every%20single%20day%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months%2C%20over%20260%20fact-checkers%2C%20reporters%20and%20editors%20collaborated%20to%20identify%20misinformation%20and%20combat%20harmful%20and%20misleading%20content%2C%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20bogus%20poll%20surveys%20and%20AI-generated%20deepfakes.%20Publishers%20joined%20in%20and%20amplified%20the%20fact-check%20content%20and%20protected%20millions%20of%20voters%20from%20poll-related%20misinformation.%20This%20election%20fact-checking%20effort%20has%20been%20supported%20by%20deepfake%20and%20synthetic%20media%20experts%20from%20renowned%20institutions%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%20(IITs)%20and%20leading%20AI%20organisations.%20These%20experts%20emphasised%20the%20crucial%20role%20that%20tools%20and%20technology%20play%20in%20debunking%20misinformation%2C%20particularly%20deepfakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20previously%20initiated%20work%20in%20the%20field%20of%20fighting%20misinformation%20has%20led%20to%20training%20and%20capacity-building%20programmes%20throughout%20India%20and%20beyond.%20Supported%20by%20the%20Google%20News%20Initiative%2C%20we%20run%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20training%20networks%2C%20which%20has%20benefited%20hundreds%20of%20newsrooms%20and%20thousands%20of%20journalists%20in%20more%20than%2010%20languages%20across%20India.%20Journalists%20within%20the%20network%20were%20chosen%20through%20an%20open-call%20process%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20implementation%20of%20Train%20the%20Trainer%20(ToT)%20programmes%20in%20various%20languages%20nationwide.%20These%20journalists%2C%20stationed%20across%20India%2C%20have%20since%20emerged%20as%20ambassadors%20of%20the%20network%20dedicated%20to%20debunking%20misinformation%20and%20fostering%20a%20robust%20information%20ecosystem.%20FactShala%2C%20India's%20largest%20media%20literacy%20network%2C%20has%20enabled%20diverse%20communities%20and%20individuals%20around%20the%20country%20with%20tools%20and%20approaches%20to%20consume%20information%20critically%20and%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20because%20of%20these%20efforts%20that%20India%20has%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20fact-checkers%20in%20the%20world%20today%20who%20are%20at%20the%20frontlines%20in%20the%20global%20fight%20against%20misinformation.%20This%20is%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%202018%2C%20when%20there%20were%20only%20two-three%20fact-checking%20organisations%20in%20the%20country.%20India%20has%2017%20International%20Fact-Checking%20Network%20(IFCN)-certified%20fact-checking%20organisations%20today.%20The%20United%20States%2C%20by%20comparison%2C%20has%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20efforts%20have%20consistently%20been%20focused%20on%20building%20resilience%20against%20misinformation%20and%20empowering%20journalists%2C%20newsrooms%20and%20engaged%20citizens%20with%20tools%20to%20fight%20the%20menace%20of%20mis-%20and%20disinformation.%20The%20goalpost%20of%20Shakti-India%20Election%20Fact%20Checking%20Collective%20aligned%20with%20this%20collaborative%20mission%20-%20to%20build%20a%20society%20that%20values%20and%20thrives%20on%20the%20critical%20consumption%20of%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20poses%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20democracy%20in%20India%20as%20misinformation%20continues%20to%20batter%20trust%20in%20democracy%20and%20its%20allied%20institutions.%20Given%20the%20number%20of%20elections%20happening%20around%20the%20world%20this%20year%2C%20it%20will%20be%20exceedingly%20challenging%20to%20identify%20and%20combat%20AI-generated%20harmful%20content%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%20Misinformation%20tactics%20travel%20fast%20from%20one%20country%20to%20another.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20newsrooms%20to%20monitor%20and%20check%20the%20content%20from%20diverse%20regional%20languages%20unless%20there%20is%20a%20concerted%20and%20focused%20collaborative%20effort%20towards%20addressing%20such%20facets%20of%20the%20larger%20information%20ecosystem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shakti%20collaboration%20provides%20significant%20insights%20and%20reveals%20emerging%20patterns%20of%20election-related%20misinformation%20in%20India%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20election%20period.%20Most%20election%20misinformation%20was%20found%20in%20visual%20content%2C%20such%20as%20images%20and%20videos.%20But%20misinformation%20also%20involved%20cloned%20voices%20of%20key%20celebrities%20and%20youth%20icons%2C%20aiming%20to%20influence%20first-time%20voters%20and%20youth.%20The%20misinformation%20campaign%20mostly%20targeted%20key%20political%20leaders%2C%20parties%20and%20their%20manifestos%2C%20and%20election%20processes%2C%20including%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%2C%20among%20others.%20While%20a%20high%20number%20of%20election-related%20deepfakes%20were%20anticipated%2C%20the%20incidents%20involving%20deepfakes%20were%20fewer%20than%20what%20was%20expected%20during%20the%20elections.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20spike%20in%20misinformation%20in%20regional%20languages%2C%20mostly%20related%20to%20EVMs%20being%20rigged%20and%20manipulated.%20There%20was%20comparatively%20less%20violence%3B%20in%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20a%20few%20states%20witnessed%20violence%20that%20largely%20contributed%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20disinformation%20and%20hate%20campaigns%2C%20including%20hateful%20songs%20on%20social%20media%2C%20which%20was%20relatively%20lower%20this%20time.%20Also%2C%20the%20misinformation%2Fdisinformation%20was%20multi-dimensional%3B%20it%20didn't%20affect%20one%20political%20party.%20All%20political%20parties%20were%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%2C%20including%20the%20ruling%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3u33k2ks_voting-generic_625x300_16_March_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DResize%3D(1230%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20from%20Indian%20elections%20about%20how%20misinformation%20vectors%20move%20from%20one%20platform%20to%20another%20and%20how%20they%20become%20viral.%20The%20insight%20can%20be%20useful%20in%20developing%20tech%20solutions%20to%20address%20election-related%20misinformation%20and%20for%20content%20monitoring%20and%20fact-checking%20elections%20in%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20change%20in%20the%20information%20landscape%20globally%2C%20it%20is%20high%20time%20we%20exemplified%20collaboration%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20resilience%20to%20minimise%20the%20impact%20of%20misinformation%20and%20foster%20a%20more%20informed%20and%20resilient%20society.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20interventions%20under%20the%20Shakti%20Collective%20is%20the%20attempt%20to%20tackle%20the%20primary%20challenge%20of%20reach%20and%20amplification%20of%20fact-checks%20to%20build%20a%20shield%20against%20misinformation.%20Fighting%20misinformation%20remains%20a%20complex%20task%20that%20will%20necessitate%20innovation%20and%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20information%20consumption%20patterns.%20Together%2C%20we%20need%20to%20stand%20guard%20at%20the%20sanctimonious%20gates%20of%20democracy%20to%20fight%20the%20demon%20of%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToni%20Morrison%20famously%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20get%20these%20jobs%20that%20you%20have%20been%20so%20brilliantly%20trained%20for%2C%20just%20remember%20that%20your%20real%20job%20is%20that%20if%20you%20are%20free%2C%20you%20need%20to%20free%20somebody%20else.%20If%20you%20have%20some%20power%2C%20then%20your%20job%20is%20to%20empower%20somebody%20else.%26quot%3B%20This%20has%20to%20be%20the%20spirit%20to%20build%20community%20surveillance%20and%20intelligence%20against%20misinformation%2C%20to%20empower%20citizens%20and%20set%20them%20free%20from%20competing%20narratives%20intended%20to%20mislead%20them%2C%20to%20guard%20them%20against%20misinformation%20intended%20to%20erode%20their%20trust%20in%20society%2C%20and%20not%20let%20devious%20actors%20dismantle%20the%20integrity%20that%20elections%20hold%20in%20a%20pluralist%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Nazakat%20is%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20DataLEADS.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717159260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3u33k2ks_voting-generic_625x300_16_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-indias-fact-checking-collective-fought-poll-time-misinformation-5787495%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%2050-plus%20organisations%2C%20comprising%20prominent%20fact-checkers%20and%20established%20newsrooms%2C%20big%20and%20small%2C%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20joined%20hands%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20collective.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-indias-fact-checking-collective-fought-poll-time-misinformation-5787495%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Model%20sues%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20over%20alleged%20assault%20on%20red%20carpet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717159080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-sawa-pontyjska-cannes-film-festival_6570457.jpg%3F20240531134717%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmodel-sues-cannes-film-festival-over-alleged-assault-on-red-carpet-13146071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Ukrainian%20model%20who%20attended%20the%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20says%20she%20is%20suing%20the%20organisers%20after%20alleging%20she%20was%20assaulted%20on%20the%20red%20carpet.%22%2C%