20in%20their%20local%20language%2C%20and%20a%20detailed%20educational%20session%20conducted%20by%20a%20local%20health%20worker.%20They%20also%20receive%20the%20health%20worker%E2%80%99s%20contact%20for%20follow-up%20sessions%20over%20the%20next%20six%20months.%20This%20comprehensive%20programme%20ensures%20that%20everyone%20has%20the%20resources%20and%20support%20needed%20to%20safely%20use%20the%20Asan%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20she%20has%20reached%20out%20to%2015%2C000%20women%20in%2060%20villages%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Kanakapura.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20single%20woman%20in%20those%20areas%20are%20using%20the%20Asan%20cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagamma%2C%2036%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Kanakapura%2C%20complained%20that%20she%20can%E2%80%99t%20wear%20her%20favourite%20white%20sarees%20fearing%20stains%20during%20her%20periods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20have%20been%20using%20the%20Asan%20cup%20for%20several%20months%20now%20and%20the%20scenario%20has%20changed.%20The%20line%20between%20the%20period%20and%20non-period%20days%20has%20blurred.%20I%20have%20recommended%20it%20to%20my%20niece%20now%20as%20well.%20The%20pads%20used%20to%20give%20me%20rashes%20on%20the%20thighs%20but%20now%20there%20are%20no%20such%20issues.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20I%20wear%20whatever%20colour%20saree%20I%20want%20without%20any%20fear%20of%20stains%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayalakshmi%2C%2038%2C%20highlighted%20that%20she%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321703%2Fiit-material-scientists-innovate-biodegradable-super-absorbent-sheets-for-sanitary-pads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20the%20used%20pads%20in%20a%20plastic%20bag%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20burn%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20other%20choice%2C%20I%20just%20burned%20them%20when%20no%20one%20was%20watching.%20But%20not%20with%20the%