n-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-239x300.jpeg%20239w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-500x627.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-768x963.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-150x188.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351293%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnchal%20Bhateja%E2%80%99s%20journey%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20widespread%20accessibility%20awareness.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInclusivity%20IRL%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20disability%20inclusion%20journey%20at%20her%20organisation%2C%20Seema%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20human%20resources%20manager%20based%20out%20of%20Delhi%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CIncluding%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20has%20helped%20the%20organisation%20in%20several%20unintended%20ways.%20Beyond%20just%20creating%20a%20more%20equitable%20workforce%2C%20having%20PwDs%20at%20the%20workplace%20has%20helped%20us%20relook%20at%20our%20policies%2C%20processes%20and%20infrastructure%20from%20a%20new%20perspective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20and%20more%20employers%20warm%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20employing%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20also%20moving%20towards%20becoming%20a%20more%20inclusive%20space%20for%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20this%20sentiment%2C%20Amar%20Jain%2C%20a%20visually%20impaired%20lawyer%20and%20accessibility%20professional%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20lawyer%20with%20a%20disability%2C%20we%20face%20enormous%20barriers.%20The%20data%20provided%20by%20cli